					<h2>Demo<?php echo ' '.$r.$s; ?>: Fixed Position Ad</h2>
					<p>Ads support the site they appear on. Keeping an ad inside the browser's viewport increases
						their value. These ads move alone fluidly as the user scrolls the content; their <code>position</code>
						changes as the page's scroll positon changes within a dynamically defined range. When the bottom
						of the content is reached, the ad stops at the bottom position until the page is scrolled back.</p>
					<p>The effect is almost unnoticable, at least at first, the user is focused on the content while the
						ad quietly stays within view.</p>
